1.2.4

  • (MSE), . . \[ MSE = \frac{1}{N}\sum_{n=1}^N (\tilde{y}_n - y_n)^2 \]

  • , (confusion matrix) .

    • (accuracy)

    • (binary classification) \[\begin{eqnarray*} {\rm Accuracy} &=& \frac{\rm TP + TN}{N} \\ {\rm Precision} &=& \frac{\rm TP}{\rm TP + FP}\\ {\rm Recall} &=& \frac{\rm TP}{\rm TP + FN} = {\rm Sensitivity}\\ {\rm Specificity} &=& \frac{\rm TN}{\rm TN + FP} \end{eqnarray*}\]
